lly mother would make what's called a syrup dumpling (flour dumpling with treacle). May be just a banana chopped up in milk. But we had a second course most dinners, unless times were bad. I've known bad times when mother was put to it to give us a proper
 meal. I remember one period, a ten week strike when I was a child and we just had to scratch what we could get. For 2d or 3d }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2233513\charrsid15301266 m}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8596504\charrsid15301266 
