\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13773995 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8596504\charrsid15301266 Were you able to get meat at all during that period when they were really tight?
