. There must have been hundreds of families for worse off than me. We were called the respectable working class. And we were taught to make the best use of them halfpenny penny that came into the house. We had it }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12718837\charrsid15301266 \{ILLEGIBLE\}}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8596504\charrsid15301266  in us 10 sticks with you too.
